review.prompt:
You have received the following PDDL solution from the orchestrator:
{pddl_solution}

Your goal is to perform a detailed audit according to your private information:
{agents->auditor->private_information}

Review the PDDL solution. Confirm that the definitions correctly reflect the initial task description, and critically assess whether the generated plan (if included) or the planning problem structure avoids relying on non-standard PDDL features or loopholes that shortcut the described causal links. If the PDDL is structurally sound and adheres strictly to preconditions/effects, confirm its validity. If errors or non-adherence to constraints are found, detail them.
